### Fuzzy Navigation System API - Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

###

### Simple Simulation - Default Parameters
POST http://localhost:8000/api/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Simulation - Single Vehicle
POST http://localhost:8000/api/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicle_types": ["Standard"],
  "max_time": 300.0
}

###

### Simulation - Custom Parameters
POST http://localhost:8000/api/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicle_types": ["Heavy", "Agile"],
  "dt": 0.05,
  "max_time": 400.0,
  "map_width": 1000.0,
  "map_height": 800.0,
  "target_x": 500.0,
  "target_y": 700.0
}

###

### Benchmark - Quick Test (5 iterations)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/benchmark
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "iterations": 5,
  "vehicle_types": ["Standard"]
}

###

### Benchmark - Full Test (30 iterations, all vehicles)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/benchmark
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "iterations": 30,
  "vehicle_types": ["Heavy", "Standard", "Agile"],
  "threads": 4
}

###

### Benchmark - High Performance (100 iterations, 8 threads)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/benchmark
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "iterations": 100,
  "threads": 8
}
